1695
01:35:59.520 --> 01:36:00.851
<i>Without those qualities.</i>

1696
01:36:00.960 --> 01:36:04.407
<i>magic. as an an' form.
would no longer exist.</i>

1697
01:36:04.960 --> 01:36:09.090
<i>But what happens if these qualities
are not used for their higher purpose?</i>

1698
01:36:09.200 --> 01:36:11.851
<i>And instead they're used to cheat. lie.</i>

1699
01:36:11.920 --> 01:36:14.161
<i>For personal gain or for greed.</i>

1700
01:36:14.560 --> 01:36:16.324
